item.description:
Reply to 'Apache POI - error in reading excel file' on stackoverflow at https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1859454/apache-poi-error-in-reading-excel-file:

POI probably has a dependency on log4j. Just include the log4j jar in your classpath.
